<p>Analyzed exhaust system performance to reduce backpressure and improve flow efficiency.</p>
<ul>
<li>Simulated exhaust gas flow behavior</li>
<li>Identified flow restrictions and optimized geometry</li>
<li>Improved overall exhaust performance</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Tools:</b> SolidWorks Flow Simulation</p>
</div>
 
